{
  "stem": "5891.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just to have a little conversation, he didn't look so mean, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, well, how are the things going out there, I said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Are you-- no, he was from the big city, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, no, my wife is dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was a little talkative, the man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I, second day, I had a little confidence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, gosh, maybe I should take one of those [INAUDIBLE] meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like dog food in the cans, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I figured I'll kind of take one of those and bring it to the girls in the block.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I didn't touch nothing till toward the end, towards just before we got out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And remember, we got those striped things on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a, like a [? cord, ?] like a [? coddle ?] type of a thing, because you always had our bowls on this, you know, and a spoon.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you had that little support there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what I did is, I took a can and I stuck it under my arm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even here you couldn't see it, you know, but I kept it over here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, you've got to march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], and those are girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is a barrack of girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they walk to you up to the left and go up the stairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You go in your barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they watch you almost going down the hall, all the way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I figured, oh god, I'm doing good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was just going to go open my door to get into that thing there, and halt!",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I turned around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I figured what the hell?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It can't be that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Must have seen, must have seen something there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Number [SPEAKING GERMAN], halt!",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
